title: PwnageTool_4.01.dmg
description:
PwnageTool 4.1 is a Mac based iPhone firmware creation tool for creating custom ipsw/firmware for various Apple handheld devices. 
This version supports the 4.0 firmware from Apple for a specific set of devices that are in a specific technical state. 
This point release fixes a bug related to iBooks.
Please visit our blog at http://blog.iphone-dev.org for further details.
